<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="330" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1899,2032]" pageId="3" pageNumber="330">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,1899,1924]" pageId="3" pageNumber="330">Remarks</emphasis>
. Found at depths of 
<quantity box="[554,673,1899,1924]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.9" metricValueMax="3.5" metricValueMin="0.3" pageId="3" pageNumber="330" unit="m" value="190.0" valueMax="350.0" valueMin="30.0">
30– 
<specimenCount box="[596,673,1899,1924]" pageId="3" pageNumber="330" type="generic">350 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
. In 
<collectingCountry box="[720,791,1899,1924]" name="Brazil" pageId="3" pageNumber="330">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[926,1038,1900,1924]" class="Malacostraca" family="Diogenidae" genus="Cancellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[926,1038,1900,1924]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="330">Cancellus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is represented only by 
<taxonomicName box="[1314,1435,1900,1923]" class="Malacostraca" family="Diogenidae" genus="Cancelus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ornatus">
<emphasis box="[1314,1435,1900,1923]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="330">C. ornatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
whose nearest relative is 
<taxonomicName box="[434,539,1935,1959]" class="Malacostraca" family="Diogenidae" genus="Cancellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridis">
<emphasis box="[434,539,1935,1959]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="330">C. viridis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Caribbean Sea. The use of limestone, calcareous algae, sponges and coral as shelter, hinders the recognition of possible new species, because field collectors, expecting to find hermit crabs in gastropod shells, may unknowingly discard 
<taxonomicName box="[673,785,2007,2031]" class="Malacostraca" family="Diogenidae" genus="Cancellus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[673,785,2007,2031]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="330">Cancellus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
specimens.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
